ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectAppointment of Ernst & Young as Auditor and the Auditor General of Canada as joint auditor of the Canada Post Corporation
PrecisOrder appointing (1) Ernst & Young as the AUDITOR of the Canada Post Corporation; and (2) the Auditor General of Canada as JOINT AUDITOR of the same Corporation, for the fiscal year ending on December 31, 2020.
